message.body: Confession: needed to know if I did indeed prefer your "don't worry baby" over the beach chicos so I went ahead and re-watched. I do indeed prefer yours.
Yea ok just thought the sweet nostalgia would work on you but apparently the world has hardened you, Luke Skidmore
Well that's disappointing
I miss you crazyass, you know it
Yo ass is crazy not my ass
Come to Philly then. Are you playing soon around here?
Your boyfriend would love that. We'll be there within 5 or 6 months
Easy... Scott's great. Which has nothing to do with you or your music which I have yet to ever see...
Tell me about him,
He's an actor too, he's a collaborator, he's steady and thoughtful. He's playful and attentive. Is that what you wanted to hear?

Absolutely. 100% honest with you, I'm thrilled to hear you say that. It's exactly what you deserve. You are all of those things and it makes my heart burst that you've found someone worthy of you. For real.
That's very sweet of you. I didn't mean to imply otherwise.
I know you. I knew what you meant.
He looks like a catch.
:) he'd love the protomen for real. Are you coming to philly or somewhere around?
Next year. Probably early march
But Philadelphia specifically?
I'm not sure. As soon as Luka knows, winnie knows
:) are you going to tour forever?
Ugh.
Allegedly.
But here's a picture of me and the lord￼
I hate you
Did he wash away your troubles while you're traveling there below?
I'll stop I'll stop
Yep, that's about right
